name: Xen Pets
description: Xen Pets are the latest addition to the Ordinals collections and are brought to life on the BTC blockchain through AI technology.  Almost perfect, these unique creatures are created with playful and colorful expressions that are sure to entice collectors. Due to their authenticity and rarity, they are a must-have for any serious Crypto collector looking to own a piece of history. Add some fun to your collection with Xen Pets. April 1st 2023.
